  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a SBC</title>

    <para>
      The <application>SBC</application> is a digital audio encoder and decoder
used to transfer data to Bluetooth audio output devices like headphones or
loudspeakers.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

